      <div xml:id="gd-p2c19q1">
        <head xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-Hd1e103"> QUESTIO 1 </head>
      <div xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-Dd1e100">
        <head xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-Hd1e102">Dictum</head>
        <p xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-d1e109"> Quod episcopus licentiam clericis adeundi monasterium dare
          debeat, in Tolletano [IV.] Concilio precipitur, in quo [c. 49.] ita statutum legitur: </p>
      </div>
        <div xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-Dd1e112">
          <head xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-Hd1e114">Caput 1</head>
          <head xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-Hd1e117" type="question-title"> Non debet negari clericis
            ingressus, qui monachorum propositum appetunt.</head>
          <p xml:id="gd-p2c19q1-d1e120"> Clerici, qui monachorum propositum appetunt, (quiameliorem
            uitam sequi cupiunt, ) liberos eis ab episcopo inmonasteriis largiri oportet ingressus
            . </p>
        </div>
      </div>
